{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.000", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.720", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.320", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.640", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die heutige Debatte beruht auf dem Betrug der Autoindustrie und dem Versagen der Bundesregierung in gleich zwei Bereichen:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.600", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens haben Sie bei der Luftreinhaltung jahrelang blind auf die Versprechen der Autoindustrie gesetzt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.520", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die neuen Autos schon weniger Schadstoffe aussto\u00dfen werden und Sie so die europ\u00e4ischen Grenzwerte einhalten k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.960", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein gro\u00dfer Irrtum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.600", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Ihnen nun aber auch schon seit Jahren bekannt ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.240", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zweitens haben Sie bei der Aufarbeitung des Abgas\u00adskandals\u00a0\u2013\u00a0\u2013"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.200", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Es ist hier vorne ein bisschen laut."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.880", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.640", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich bedaure sehr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.080", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie mich darauf hinweisen m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.800", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es hier sehr unruhig ist.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.240", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bitte die Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.680", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Rednerin zuzuh\u00f6ren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.120", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch wenn wir jetzt schon zu vorger\u00fcckter Stunde sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.640", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Noch einmal: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.680", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen es wirklich schaffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.440", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vor 24\u00a0Uhr zum Ende zu kommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.960", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.720", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben das Wort, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.720", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und ich greife das n\u00e4chste Mal viel fr\u00fcher ein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.360", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danke.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.400", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zweitens haben Sie bei der Aufarbeitung des Abgasskandals auf ganzer Linie versagt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.440", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben mit der Autoindustrie einen schmutzigen Deal gemacht: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.720", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Hersteller haben sich zu einem Softwareupdate mit geringer Wirkung verpflichtet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.320", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Gegenzug verzichtet die Bundesregierung darauf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.320", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Rechtswidrigkeit der Manipulation festzustellen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.840", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Ergebnis der Aussitzerei durch die Bundesregierung schichtet sie ein Problem auf das n\u00e4chste. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.920", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die seit 2010 geltenden Grenzwerte werden immer noch nicht eingehalten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.440", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine Klage der EU-Kommission steht quasi vor der T\u00fcr."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.920", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Gesundheit der Bev\u00f6lkerung wird weiter hoch belastet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.480", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die betrogenen Dieselbesitzer haben schon jetzt einen erheblichen Wertverlust ihres Autos erlitten und m\u00fcssen nach dem Urteil des Bundesverwaltungsgerichts auch noch bef\u00fcrchten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.040", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bald nicht mehr in die Innenst\u00e4dte fahren zu d\u00fcrfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.960", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit diesem wegen Ihrer Unt\u00e4tigkeit wachsenden Problem verh\u00f6hnen Sie die B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.120", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit unserem Antrag zeigen wir als Linke einen rechtlichen Weg auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.240", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Sie den gordischen Knoten Ihres schmutzigen Deals in vern\u00fcnftiger Weise l\u00f6sen k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.680", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Kraftfahrt-Bundesamt hat mit der europ\u00e4ischen Fahrzeuggenehmigungsverordnung eine Grundlage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.280", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die dazu erm\u00e4chtigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.960", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Hersteller zu einer Hardwarenachr\u00fcstung zu verpflichten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.040", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liegt n\u00e4mlich ein erhebliches Risiko f\u00fcr die \u00f6ffentliche Gesundheit vor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.800", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist das KBA sogar befugt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.640", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Typengenehmigung zu widerrufen oder zu entziehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.640", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das hei\u00dft das Auto stillzulegen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.440", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Umweltbundesamt best\u00e4tigt noch einmal das erhebliche Risiko f\u00fcr die \u00f6ffentliche Gesundheit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.280", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unabh\u00e4ngig davon, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.520", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was hier heute Abend f\u00fcr ein Mist losgelassen wurde.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.600", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Entschuldigung!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.120", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht in seiner neuesten Studie davon aus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.360", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass in Deutschland 6\u00a0000\u00a0Menschen aufgrund der Belastung mit Stickoxiden vorzeitig sterben und dass 8\u00a0Prozent der bestehenden Diabetes-mellitus-Erkrankungen auf Stickoxide in der Au\u00dfenluft zur\u00fcckzuf\u00fchren sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.240", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei Asthmaerkrankungen sind es sogar rund 14\u00a0Prozent."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.640", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie viele Gr\u00fcnde braucht die Bundesregierung denn noch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.120", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die massive Gesundheitsbelastung der Bev\u00f6lkerung schnellstens zu beenden?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.400", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nat\u00fcrlich wollen wir daf\u00fcr nicht die Fahrzeuge stilllegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.600", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch wenn das hier heute behauptet wurde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.920", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das k\u00e4me ja einer Enteignung von Millionen Dieselbesitzern gleich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.560", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.000", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie endlich sauber werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.680", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00a7\u00a025 Absatz\u00a02 der EG-Fahrzeuggenehmigungsverordnung sieht vor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.160", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das KBA bei fehlender Vorschriftsm\u00e4\u00dfigkeit von Fahrzeugen im Wege einer Anordnung nachtr\u00e4glich Nebenbestimmungen erlassen kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.040", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die Vorschriftsm\u00e4\u00dfigkeit wiederherzustellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.080", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aus unserer Sicht muss als Nebenbestimmung die Hardwarenachr\u00fcstung der Fahrzeuge gefordert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.480", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das w\u00e4re gerecht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.720", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt also im bestehenden Recht eine Grundlage daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.520", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Autoindustrie zu verpflichten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.440", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihre Fahrzeuge wirklich wirksam nachzur\u00fcsten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.640", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die Gelder daf\u00fcr sind aufseiten der Industrie vorhanden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.440", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "BMW, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.520", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daimler und VW haben allein im vergangenen Jahr nach Steuern \u00fcber 30\u00a0Milliarden Euro Gewinn gemacht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.120", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was fehlt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.040", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist der politische Wille der Bundesregierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.840", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "endlich zu handeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.560", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Andernfalls wird Deutschland wohl schon in der n\u00e4chsten Woche von der EU-Kommission wegen der Nichteinhaltung der Grenzwerte teuer verklagt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.680", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das v\u00f6llig zu Recht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.960", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt also eine geeignete Ma\u00dfnahme, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "281.760", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es gibt eine Rechtsgrundlage zur Anordnung dieser Ma\u00dfnahme, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "281.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.080", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und es gibt eine ausreichende Finanzierungsgrundlage der Autoindustrie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "286.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.960", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was noch fehlt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "286.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.720", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist die im Gesetz vorgesehene Strafe f\u00fcr die Autoindustrie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.480", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dar\u00fcber sprechen wir ein anderes Mal."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "293.560", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "293.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "294.400", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kommen Sie bitte zum Schluss."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "294.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "295.000", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "295.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "296.320", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Bundeskanzlerin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "296.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "297.120", 
   "id": "s000086", 
